---
import BaseLayout from '../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Disclaimer — BKK Songkran" description="Disclaimer for BKK Songkran.com. We are an independent guide, not affiliated with any Songkran festival organiser." canonical="https://bkksongkran.com/disclaimer">

  <section class="pt-36 pb-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <div class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-3" style="color:#006479;">Legal</div>
      <h1 class="font-headline font-extrabold tracking-tighter mb-2" style="font-size:clamp(2.5rem,6vw,4rem);color:#003345;line-height:0.95;">Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="text-sm mb-12" style="color:#6b8fa3;">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color:#326177;">

        <div class="rounded-2xl p-5" style="background:#FFF8E0;border:1px solid rgba(255,159,10,0.3);">
          <p class="font-semibold" style="color:#92400E;">BKK Songkran is an independent fan guide and is <strong>not affiliated with, endorsed by, or representing</strong> S2O Festival, Siam Songkran, GCircuit, or any other event organiser, venue, ticket platform, hotel, airline, or Thai government authority.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Festival information</h2>
          <p>Lineup, schedule, pricing, and venue information is compiled from publicly available sources and may not reflect last-minute changes. Always verify directly with official festival websites and social media channels before purchasing tickets or making plans.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Transport and safety</h2>
          <p>Road closure information, BTS/MRT schedules, and transport guidance are based on historical data and announced plans. Conditions during Songkran can change rapidly. Always check with the Bangkok Mass Transit Authority (BMTA), BTS, MRT, and Thai traffic authorities for live updates. BKK Songkran accepts no liability for disruption to your travel.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">AI guide (Nong)</h2>
          <p>The Nong AI guide is powered by OpenAI's GPT-4o model and is provided for general informational entertainment only. Responses may occasionally be inaccurate, outdated, or incomplete. Do not rely solely on the AI guide for time-sensitive decisions such as transport, medical advice, legal matters, or emergency situations.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Personal safety</h2>
          <p>Songkran is a joyful celebration but can involve large crowds, alcohol, water activities, and heat. BKK Songkran provides general safety tips for informational purposes. We are not responsible for personal injury, theft, illness, or any harm that occurs during your attendance at any event or public area. Travel insurance is strongly recommended.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">No commercial relationship</h2>
          <p>Links to external ticketing platforms, hotels, or services do not constitute endorsement and we receive no commission from purchases made through this site (unless explicitly stated). Prices shown are approximate and subject to change.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg mb-3" style="color:#003345;">Contact</h2>
          <p>If you spot an error or have a concern, use the feedback form on the site.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
